#

Truffle Scrambled Eggs with Asparagus

$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

EggsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchLuxury

Description

Indulge in a creamy, luxurious blend of eggs and asparagus, enhanced with the earthy aroma of truffle oil.

Ingredients

  • Eggs: 4 large
  • Asparagus: 1 cup, trimmed and cut into 1-inch pieces
  • Heavy cream: 2 tablespoons
  • Truffle oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Butter: 1 tablespoon
  • Fresh chives: for garnish
